- **libnetsnmp**: licensed under the [Net-SNMP License](https://github.com/net-snmp/net-snmp/blob/master/COPYING).
- **libnetsnmpagent**: licensed under the [Net-SNMP License](https://github.com/net-snmp/net-snmp/blob/master/COPYING).

The full license for each library can be found in the links above.
